      "date": "2014-04-29 07:34:06.000000000",
      "message": "Abandoned\n\nSince using dir entry pointer to resolve hash conflict will involve complicate lock issue, I will instead using same_hash_offset to solve hash conflict issue. i.e. merge 9699 and 10109 to 9191.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
